These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, dog, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, taxi, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk | juice    | 7up       |
| Pet         | frog | goat    | dog      | cat |
| Transport   | scooter   | taxi | tram | ship        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, onion, lemon, blueberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, designer, chef, engineer
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, helicopter, bus, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the engineer##1
2. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the chef is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the ship is the security-guard##1
6. the person driving the boat is the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | lemon   | onion | garlic     | blueberry      |
| Job         | designer | chef | engineer | security-guard |
| Transport   | helicopter    | boat   | bus     | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, sudoku, fishing, reading
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, funk, classical, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, turkish, australian, colombian
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the turkish is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of classical##1
5. the colombian is on the right of the fan of funk##1
6. the colombian is on the right of the australian##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | card-games | sudoku | fishing | reading |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | funk    | techno | classical     |
| Nationality   | thai | australian    | colombian | turkish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, dancer, writer, librarian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, water-polo, lacrosse
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, bus, subway
1. the writer is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
4. the dancer is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is the writer##1
7. the writer is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
8. the librarian is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | nurse | librarian | writer | dancer |
| Sport       | skateboarding     | lacrosse      | golf     | water-polo      |
| Transport   | scooter | boat         | subway      | bus        |

