.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, collecting, chess, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, adventure, action, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, basketball, water-polo, golf
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person watching action movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person watching adventure movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | chess   | writing | collecting  | traveling      |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | family        | crime  | adventure       |
| Sport         | soccer | water-polo    | basketball | golf |

