.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, security-guard, entrepreneur, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, adventure, comedy, documentary
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, pop, salsa, electronic
1. the pilot is the fan of pop##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the chef##1
4. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1
5. the security-guard is on the far left##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is the entrepreneur##1
7. the fan of pop is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
8. the chef is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | security-guard | entrepreneur | chef | pilot |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary   | comedy  | adventure | musical   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | hip-hop     | salsa | pop       |

