.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, pear, cabbage, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, dancing, traveling, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, family, animation, adventure
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person watching family movies is the person eating cabbage##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | lettuce  | strawberry | cabbage   | pear     |
| Hobby         | singing | dancing   | photography  | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | animation         | western  | family | adventure  |

