The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, documentary, family, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, spanish, american, colombian
1. the person drinking mirinda is the american##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the american##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
6. the colombian is the person drinking milk##1
7. the spanish is on the left of the colombian##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | water | milk     | tea | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | satire  | sports | family       | documentary    |
| Nationality   | spanish   | colombian | dutch    | american |

