.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, cherry, strawberry, lemon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, country, hip-hop, electronic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, rugby, biathlon, weightlifting
1. the fan of country is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person eating cherry##1
5. the person eating cherry is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | strawberry        | lemon   | cherry  | carrot   |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | electronic     | country    | hip-hop       |
| Sport         | rugby | parkour | biathlon | weightlifting |

