.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, cola, water
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, cranberry, onion, eggplant
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, fish, cat, horse
1. the person drinking water is the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person eating onion is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | cola | water | milk        |
| Food       | eggplant | pomegranate  | cranberry | onion     |
| Pet        | fish    | cat   | horse  | guinea-pig |

