.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, pilot, dancer, librarian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, sailing, skiing, cycling
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, trike, train
1. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the pilot##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the left of the librarian##1
7. the person who's sport is soccer is the person driving the trike##1
8. the person who's sport is skiing is the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | lawyer  | librarian | pilot  | dancer |
| Sport       | skiing | sailing        | cycling | soccer       |
| Transport   | boat   | subway          | train          | trike       |

