.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, collecting, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, thriller, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, thai, russian, french
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the french is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the russian##1
7. the french is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping   | collecting   | magic-tricks | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | comedy | drama   | zombie |
| Nationality   | french     | mexican  | russian  | thai  |

