.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, puzzles, drawing, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, jazz, indie, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, surfing, volleyball, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the fan of soul##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | board-games | puzzles    | dancing        | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | indie     | soul        | ambient   |
| Sport         | surfing   | climbing | volleyball | rugby  |

