.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, satire, fantasy
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, british, argentine, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, taxi, snowmobile
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the argentine##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the japanese##1
3. the dutch is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
8. the british is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | fantasy  | action    | satire    |
| Nationality   | japanese | argentine  | dutch  | british |
| Transport     | snowmobile  | quad-bike | taxi | trike        |

