.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, sprite, cola
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, musical, drama, horror
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, parkour, surfing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person watching horror movies is the person drinking cola##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is the person watching zombie movies##1
8. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade        | cola    | almond-milk | sprite      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie        | horror   | musical  | drama  |
| Sport         | lacrosse | parkour | surfing   | sailing |

