The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, comedy, action, adventure
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, snake, rat
1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is the owner of the snake##1
5. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
6. the person watching action movies is the person eating pepper##1
7. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | cabbage     | spinach   | pepper | pomegranate |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | adventure | action | comedy   |
| Pet           | rat    | goldfish     | cat      | snake     |

