3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the malaysian##1
4. the fan of gospel is the malaysian##1
5. the teacher is on the far left##1
6. the freelancer is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the japanese is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
