.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, canadian, argentine, dutch
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, weightlifting, lacrosse
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, skateboard, helicopter
1. the canadian is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
7. the argentine is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | canadian | argentine | dutch |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket | lacrosse  | weightlifting  |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship | helicopter     | skateboard  |

