.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, writer, teacher, electrician
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, brazilian, colombian, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, cycling, basketball
1. the writer is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the teacher##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is on the far right##1
5. the dutch is the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the spanish is on the far left##1
7. the electrician is on the far right##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | writer  | teacher  | chef | electrician |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch | brazilian   | colombian      |
| Sport         | weightlifting | cycling    | skateboarding   | basketball         |

 